@startuml SequenceDiagram_ProxyFacade
title Sequence Diagram — Proxy (Cache) + Facade Pattern\nGetAlbums: cache miss → cache hit → write invalidation

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor White

actor "User" as User

participant ": FormMain"             as FM
participant ": CachingFacebookProxy" as Proxy
participant ": FacebookManager"      as Facade
participant ": FacebookService"      as SDK

== First call — cache miss ==

User  ->  FM    : buttonLoadAlbums_Click()
activate FM
FM    ->  Proxy : GetAlbums()
activate Proxy

note over Proxy : m_CachedAlbums == null → cache miss

Proxy ->  Facade : GetAlbums()
activate Facade
Facade ->  SDK   : user.Albums  [Graph API call — takes time]
activate SDK
SDK   --> Facade : AlbumCollection
deactivate SDK
Facade --> Proxy  : List<Album>
deactivate Facade
Proxy ->  Proxy  : m_CachedAlbums = result
Proxy --> FM     : List<Album>
deactivate Proxy
deactivate FM

== Second call — cache hit ==

User  ->  FM    : (another feature reads albums)
activate FM
FM    ->  Proxy : GetAlbums()
activate Proxy

note over Proxy : m_CachedAlbums != null → cache hit\nNo API call made

Proxy --> FM : m_CachedAlbums
deactivate Proxy
deactivate FM

== Write operation — cache invalidation ==

User  ->  FM    : upload photo to album
activate FM
FM    ->  Proxy : UploadPhotoToAlbum(album, filePath)
activate Proxy
Proxy ->  Facade : UploadPhotoToAlbum(album, filePath)
activate Facade
Facade ->  SDK   : [Graph API upload — takes time]
activate SDK
SDK   --> Facade : success
deactivate SDK
Facade --> Proxy  : success
deactivate Facade
Proxy ->  Proxy  : r_CachedAlbumPhotos.Remove(albumId)
Proxy ->  Proxy  : m_CachedAlbums = null
Proxy --> FM     : success
deactivate Proxy
deactivate FM
@enduml
